WEBVTT

01:28:51.358 --> 01:28:54.649
How many times have I asked you
to renovate our house?

01:28:54.899 --> 01:28:56.274
Oh, is that
what's bothering you?

01:28:56.316 --> 01:28:57.774
We're going to do it now,
aren't we?

01:28:58.233 --> 01:29:00.524
Even their kitchen
is as big as our whole house!
